title: UNI's Schult named MVC Defensive Player of the Week
text:
UNI's Schult named MVC Defensive Player of the Week Posted: Panthers Get the latest news and sports information about the University of Northern Iowa Panthers sports teams, including football, basketball, volleyball, baseball and softball. More >> Get the latest news and sports information about the University of Northern Iowa Panthers sports teams, including football, basketball, volleyball, baseball and softball. More >> CEDAR FALLS (KWWL) - 
UNI's Karter Schult earned Missouri Valley Defensive Player of the Week honors following the Panthers' win at 6th ranked South Dakota State on Saturday. 
Schult led a defense that allowed just one score out of a high powered Jackrabbit offense. The junior tallied 7 total tackles, including 3 sacks. He also created first contact on a South Dakota State runner during a 4th down stop that sealed the UNI victory. 
The Tripoli native leads the Missouri Valley in sacks and tackles for loss this season.
